0and%20more%20than%201%20million%20shares%20worth%20over%20%24400%20million%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%20and%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20holdings%20of%20Simons'%20Renaissance%20Technologies%20went%20from%20fewer%20than%204%2C000%20shares%20at%20the%20end%20of%20March%2C%20to%201.9%20million%20three%20months%20later.%20It%20still%20owned%201.2%20million%20Nvidia%20shares%20worth%20%24526%20million%20on%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhilippe%20Laffont's%20Coatue%20Management%20counted%20the%20chipmaker%20as%20its%20biggest%20public-market%20position%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20after%20the%20firm%20increased%20its%20stake%20by%20more%20than%20a%20million%20shares%20over%20the%20preceding%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlen%20Kacher's%20Light%20Street%20had%20Nvidia%20as%20the%20biggest%20position%20in%20its%20public%20portfolio%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20after%20first%20investing%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202022.%20The%20stake%20has%20driven%20the%20firm's%20strong%20returns%20this%20year%2C%20which%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20firm%20told%20Business%20Insider%20was%2034.1%25%20for%20its%20long-short%20fund%20and%2044.5%25%20for%20its%20long-only%20offering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Chase%20Coleman's%20Tiger%20Global%20added%20more%20than%20a%20million%20shares%20of%20Nvidia%20to%20its%20book%20after%20not%20owning%20it%2012%20months%20earlier.%20Maverick%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20increased%20its%20Nvidia%20stake%2010-fold%20since%20the%20start%20of%202022's%20third%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETudor%20Investment%20Corporation%20also%20grew%20its%20position%20from%20fewer%20than%208%2C000%20shares%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%20to%20179%2C000%20shares%20worth%20about%20%2476%20million%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20ignoring%20options.%20However%2C%20it%20slashed%20its%20holdings%20to%20fewer%20than%2015%2C000%20shares%20worth%20about%20%246%20million%20by%20the%20end%20of%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%