%20social%20media%20appeals%20by%20the%20Indian%20student%20community%20in%20the%20UK%20after%20the%20Sikh%20student%20was%20reported%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20a%20tragic%2C%20heartbreaking%20loss%20of%20one%20of%20our%20beautiful%20lives.%20I%20had%20spoken%20to%20his%20father%20and%20friends%20only%20some%20days%20ago%20when%20we%20first%20found%20out%20he%20was%20missing%20and%20had%20been%20praying%20for%20his%20safe%20discovery%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sanam%20Arora%2C%20Chair%20of%20the%20National%20Indian%20Students%20and%20Alumni%20Union%20(NISAU)%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20thoughts%20are%20with%20his%20family%20%26amp%3B%20friends.%20Requesting%20all%20to%20please%20say%20a%20prayer%20for%20the%20departed%20soul%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatia%20was%20pursuing%20an%20MSc%20in%20Digital%20Finance%20at%20Loughborough%20University.%20After%20he%20went%20missing%20last%20week%2C%20his%20case%20was%20also%20flagged%20with%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Manjinder%20Singh%20Sirsa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDeeply%20saddened%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20passing%20of%20G.S.%20Bhatia%2C%20a%20Loughborough%20University%20student%20who%20was%20missing%20since%20Dec%2015th.%20Our%20thoughts%20are%20with%20the%20family%20and%20friends%20during%20this%20difficult%20time.%20May%20Waheguru%20give%20strength%20to%20his%20parents%20mourning%20this%20profound%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Sirsa%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703149740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F18qe20ss_missing-indian-student-gurashman-singh-bhatia-_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fmissing-indian-student-gurashman-singh-bhati