0Johar's%20chat%20show%20%3Ci%3EKoffee%20With%20Karan%208%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20Ajay%20Devgn%20and%20Rohit%20Shetty%20talked%20about%20their%20fathers%20and%20their%20respective%20film%20journeys.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-ajay-devgn-on-nysa-being-papped-dont-like-it-but-cant-change-it-4714855%5C%22%3EAjay%20Devgn%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20how%20his%20late%20father%20and%20action%20director%20Veeru%20Devgan%20came%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20how%20he%20got%20into%20films.%20%26quot%3BHe%20ran%20away%20when%20he%20was%2013.%20He%20came%20to%20Mumbai%20without%20a%20train%20ticket.%20He%20was%20taken%20behind%20bars.%20He%20had%20no%20work%20so%20no%20food.%20Somebody%20helped%20him%2C%20said%20that%20you%20wash%20my%20cab%20every%20day%20and%20I%20will%20let%20you%20sleep%20in%20it.%20So%2C%20he%20started%20from%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajay%20Devgn%20said.%20He%20recalled%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20started%20from%20there%20and%20eventually%20became%20a%20carpenter.%20Then%20he%20became%20one%20of%20the%20gangsters%20in%20Sion-Koliwada%20area.%20He%20was%20a%20carpenter%20also%20and%20there%20were%20gang%20wars.%20One%20day%20a%20very%20senior%20action%20director%2C%20Mr%20Ravi%20Khanna%2C%20was%20passing%20by%20and%20there%20was%20this%20street%20fight%20going%20on.%20So%2C%20he%20stopped%20the%20car%20and%20called%20my%20dad%20after%20the%20fight%20and%20asked%2C%20what%20do%20you%20do%3F%20And%20he%20said%20I'm%20a%20carpenter%20here.%20So%2C%20he%20said%20one%20very%20good%20line%2C%20%3Ci%3ETu%20ladta%20achha%20hai%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20come%20and%20meet%20me%20tomorrow%20and%20made%20him%20a%20fighter.%20So%20that's%20where%20he%20started%20from%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Shetty's%20father%20MB%20Shetty%20was%20a%20stuntman%20and%20action%20choreographer%20as%20well.%20The%20filmmaker%20revealed%20that%20he%20lost%20his%20father%20at%20a%20very%20early%20stage%20in%20his%20life.%20%26quot%3BThings%20were%20difficult.%20Till%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20we%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20struggles.%20When%20I%20was%2017%2C%20I%20joined%20him%20(Ajay)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Speaking%20of%20his%20mom%20Ratna%20Shetty%2C%20the%20filmmaker%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20a%20stunt%20artist.%20That's%20how%20my%20dad%20and%20mom%20met.%20After%20he%20passed%20away%2C%20there%20was%20financial%20crisis.%20So%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20junior%20artist%20and%20after%20that%20when%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20it%20is%20a%20proper%20blockbuster%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20his%20father's%20journey%2C%20Rohit%20Shetty%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20in%20Udupi.%20He%20was%2013%20when%20he%20came%20to%20Mumbai.%20He%20was%20a%20waiter%20in%20Cotton%20Green%2C%20in%20a%20restaurant%20and%20from%20there%20he%20started.%20Then%20he%20started%20boxing%20and%20bodybuilding%2C%20and%20then%20obviously%2C%20because%20he%20was%20well-built%2C%206'3%2C%20someone%20gave%20him%20an%20idea%20why%20don't%20you%20try%20in%20movies.%20And%20then%20he%20joined...Senior%20to%20Ravi%20Khanna%20Sir%20was%20one%20action%20director%20of%20black%20and%20white%20movies%20called%20Azim%20Bhai%2C%20so%20he%20joined%20him%20and%20gradually%20he%20became%20fight%20choreographer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-ajay-devgn-on-wife-kajol-ranveer-singh-and-bollywood-parties-4714653%5C%22%3EAjay%20Devgn%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%20to%20this%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20you%20go%20on%20social%20media%2C%20read%20so%20many%20things%20like%20nepotism%20etc%20but%20people%20don't%20realise%20that%20the%20generations%20have%20worked%20very%2C%20very%20hard%20to%20reach%20till%20here.%20It's%20not%20an%20easy%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20KJo%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20laugh%20Ajay.%20My%20father%20(Yash%20Johar)%2C%20who%20is%20no%20more%2C%20would%20have%20had%20the%20biggest%20laugh%20if%20he%20read%20that%20they%20call%20me%20the%