nment%20led%20by%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20being%20called%20%E2%80%9Canti-nationals%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-alleges-khalistani-agenda-behind-farmer-protests-says-congress-playing-with-fire%2F553292%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CKhalistanis%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%E2%80%9Canarchists%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20farmers%20%E2%80%93%20many%20from%20the%20Jat%20community%20%E2%80%93%20stood%20their%20ground%20and%20spent%20their%20days%20under%20worn-out%20canvas%20tents%2C%20eating%20from%20makeshift%20kitchens%20and%20by%20facing%20off%20with%20the%20police%20who%20routinely%20tried%20to%20clear%20the%20road.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20earthen%20pots%20contain%20soil%20from%20villages%20and%20farmlands%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20Back%20in%20March%202021%2C%20when%20I%20travelled%20with%20farmer%20outfits%20and%20covered%20a%20journey%20of%20more%20than%20650%20kms%20from%20southern%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Banswara%20to%20the%20Shahjahanpur%20border%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20collective%20camaraderie%20among%20farmers%2C%20who%20spoke%20about%20the%20threat%20they%20felt%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fexplained-what-are-the-three-farm-laws-and-what-made-them-controversial-7738991.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree%20farm%20laws%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20They%20called%20the%20exercise%20of%20collecting%20soil%20in%20these%20pots%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emitti%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Esatyagraha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20satyagraha%20of%20the%20soil%2C%20a%20movement%20based%20on%20Gandhian%20principles%20of%20non-violent%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20I%20heard%20Vice-President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%E2%80%99s%20angry%20diatribe%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20wherein%20he%20asserted%20his%20identity%20as%20a%20farmer%20and%20Jat%20while%20condemning%20a%20video%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fshameful-ridiculous-unacceptable-jagdeep-dhankar-slams-trinamool-mp-kalyan-banerjee-for-mimicry-act-hits-out-at-rahul-gandhi-for-making-video%2Farticleshow%2F106127501.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20mimicking%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20think%20of%20my%20fellow%20farmers%20in%20the%20Shahjahanpur%20protests%2C%20who%20despite%20being%20ridiculed%20and%20vilified%20so%20frequently%20by%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20got%20little%20by%20way%20of%20support%20from%20figures%20such%20as%20Dhankhar%2C%20who%20at%20that%20point%20was%20the%20Governor%20of%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20far%20from%20playing%20the%20victim%20card%2C%20they%20tenaciously%20continued%20their%20satyagraha%20against%20the%20three%20laws%20till%20they%20were%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20angry%20outburst%2C%20Dhankhar%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1988365%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehis%20background%20as%20a%20Jat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20being%20from%20the%20farming%20class%20was%20being%20%E2%80%98insulted.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20individual%2C%20take%20on%20me%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20on%20my%20background%20as%20a%20farmer%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20on%20my%20background%20as%20a%20community%20member.%20Institution%20of%20Chairman%20has%20been%20ravaged%20and%20that%20too%20by%20a%20political%20party%20that%20has%20gone%20so%20far%20that%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20a%20senior%20one%2C%20videographs%20the%20other%20member%E2%80%A6%20On%20Instagram%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20your%20party%20put%20a%20video%20which%20was%20withdrawn%20later.%20That%20was%20a%20shame%20to%20me.%20You%20used%20the%20official%20Twitter%20handle%20of%20the%20spokesperson%20to%20demean%20me%2C%20insult%20me%2C%20insult%20my%20background%20as%20a%20farmer%2C%20my%20position%20as%20a%20Jat%2C%20insult%20my%20position%20as%20Chairman.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20worth%20mentioning%20that%20the%20protests%20outside%20the%20parliament%20by%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20being%20held%20at%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20unprecedented%20instance%20of%20the%20suspension%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F141-opposition-mps-suspended-so-far-are-they-allowed-to-enter-parliament-check-list-of-restrictions-11703057026922.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E143%20MPs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20which%20Dhankhar%20too%20played%20his%20part%20by%20suspending%20opposition%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20who%20were%20demanding%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20over%20the%20recent%20intrusion%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Dhankhar%20suspended%20the%20house%20as%20well%20as%20its%20members%2C%20he%20clearly%20does%20not%20want%20to%20face%20any%20criticism%2C%20citing%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20holds%20a%20constitutional%20post.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20issue%20snowballed%20into%20a%20controversy%2C%20Dhankhar%20has%20found%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-dials-vp-dhankhar-as-mimicry-row-heats-up-expresses-pain-over-abject-theatrics-101703046457739.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esupport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20PM%20Modi%2C%20and%20even%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu.%20While%20many%20would%20argue%20that%20mimicking%20is%20an%20acceptable%20form%20of%20criticism%20and%20that%20even%20if%20he%20is%20on%20a%20constitutional%20post%2C%20he%20is%20not%20beyond%20criticism%2C%20by%20invoking%20his%20caste%20and%20farming%20background%2C%20Dhankhar%20has%20created%20an%20impression%20that%20criticising%20him%20is%20the%20criticism%20of%20the%20farming%20class.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20here%2C%20that%20I%20would%20like%20to%20disagree%20with%20the%20honourable%20vice-president.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20fellow%20Jat%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20whose%20primary%20occupation%20has%20been%20farming%20for%20several%20generations%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20notice%20the%20clear%20double%20standards%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20seeing%20one%20section%20of%20Jat%20farmers%20under%20the%20anti-national%20lens%20while%20crying%20foul%20and%20asserting%20one%E2%80%99s%20Jat%20identity%20when%20convenient.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20V-P%20Dhankhar%20has%20forgotten%20that%20when%20medalled%20wrestlers%20who%20are%20also%20daughters%20of%20Jat%20farmers%2C%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fwrestlers-protest-against-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-hanging-on-in-troubled-hunt-for-justice%2Farticle67004574.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprotesting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20a%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20there%20were%20concerted%20efforts%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20the%20sportspersons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Jat%20outfits%20across%20the%20country%20stood%20firmly%20behind%20the%20sportspersons%20at%20the%20time%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20hear%20a%20similar%20emotive%20speech%20from%20Dhankhar%20on%20the%20targeted%20harassment%20of%20Jat%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20Congress%20MP%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20without%20naming%20Gandhi%2C%20Dhankhar%20slammed%20him%20for%20re