%202019%20it%20was%20abuse%20of%20power%20and%20obstruction%20of%20Congress%2C%20in%202021%20it%20was%20incitement%20of%20insurrection)%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdonald-trump-cleared-by-us-senate-of-inciting-capitol-riots%2Fa-56561629%5C%22%3ESenate%20acquitted%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20if%20the%20Senate%2C%20the%20higher%20chamber%20of%20Congress%2C%20convicts%20a%20president%20is%20he%20or%20she%20removed%20from%20office%2C%20a%20step%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdisqualification%20to%20hold%20and%20enjoy%20any%20office%20of%20honour%2C%20trust%20or%20profit%20under%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%9D%20again%2C%20as%20stipulated%20in%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20double-impeachment%20is%20no%20legal%20hindrance.%20But%20what%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdonald-trump-faces-criminal-charges%2Fa-65192807%5C%22%3ETrump%E2%80%99s%20other%20troubles%20with%20the%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20sexual%20assault%20to%20attempting%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trials%20about%20to%20start%20against%20Trump%20in%202024%20include%20civil%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjudge-to-trump-this-is-a-courtroom-not-a-political-rally%2Fa-67322515%5C%22%3Efraud%20trials%20related%20to%20how%20Trump%20and%20his%20sons%20ran%20the%20family%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20sexual%20assault%20and%20defamation%20trial.%20In%20the%20latter%20case%2C%20a%20jury%20had%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftrump-found-liable-in-e-jean-carroll-defamation-suit%2Fa-66741217%5C%22%3Efound%20Trump%20liable%20for%20defaming%20a%20former%20columnist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20judge%20concluding%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ftrump-rape-trial-columnist-carroll-4974ef026f