0at%20the%20iconic%20Gopaldas%20building%20in%20Delhi's%20Connaught%20Place.%20As%20many%20as%2016%20fire%20engines%20have%20been%20rushed%20to%20the%20spot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fvideo-fire-at-iconic-gopaldas-building-at-delhis-connaught-place-4715069%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fvideo-fire-at-iconic-gopaldas-building-at-delhis-connaught-place-4715069%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fvideo-fire-at-iconic-gopaldas-building-at-delhis-connaught-place-4715069%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samsung%20brings%20this%20Apple%20Watch%20feature%20to%20its%20smartwatches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703146050000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106177642%2Cimgsize-43600.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fsamsung-brings-this-apple-watch-feature-to-its-own-smartwatches%2Farticleshow%2F106177642.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Samsung%20has%20added%20a%20medication%20tracking%20feature%20to%20the%20Samsung%20Health%20app.%20The%20feature%20allows%20users%20to%20easily%20log%20and%20manage%20both%20prescription%20and%20over-the-counter%20medications.%20Users%20can%20enter%20the%20name%20of%20a%20medication%20to%20get%20detailed%20information%20about%20it%2C%20including%20descriptions%20and%20possible%20side%20effects.%20They%20can%20also%20log%20the%20shape%20and%20color%20of%20their%20medications%20for%20easy%20identification.%20The%20feature%20includes%20alerts%20to%20remind%20users%20when%20to%20take%20their%20medications%20and%20when%20to%20refill%20them.%20Galaxy%20Watch%20users%20will%20also%20receive%20reminders%20on%20their%20wrist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fsamsung-brings-this-apple-watch-feature-to-its-own-smartwatches%2Farticleshow%2F106177642.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22H-1B%20Visa%20Pilot%20Programme%3A%20Dates%2C%20Eligibility%20Criteria%2C%20Application%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20is%20introducing%20a%20pilot%20programme%20to%20restart%20the%20renewal%20process%20for%20qualified%20H-1B%20non-immigrant%20visa%20applicants%20within%20the%20country.%20This%20initiative%20aims%20to%20assess%20the%20Department's%20technical%20and%20operational%20capabilities%20in%20reinstating%20domestic%20visa%20renewals.%20The%20first%20phase%20is%20for%2020%2C000%20people%20and%20is%20open%20only%20to%20Indians%20and%20Canadians.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EH-1B%20Visa%20Pilot%20Programme%3A%20Dates%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20State%20Department%20will%20receive%20applications%20for%20the%20H-1B%20pilot%20programme%20from%20January%2029%20to%20April%201%2C%202024.%20Eligible%20applicants%20are%20encouraged%20to%20apply%20online%20within%20the%20three-month%20application%20window.%20The%20department%20has%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20midnight%20on%20April%2015%2C%202024%2C%20to%20submit%20written%20comments%20and%20related%20materials.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20plans%20to%20open%20approximately%204%2C000%20application%20slots%20for%20H-1B%20visa%20renewals%20every%20week.%20These%20slots%20will%20be%20available%20on%20the%20following%20dates%3A%20January%2029%2C%20February%205%2C%20February%2012%2C%20February%2019%2C%20and%20February%2026.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EH-1B%20Visa%20Pilot%20Programme%3A%20Eligibility%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnApplicants%20must%20meet%20the%20following%20criteria%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOnly%20H-1B%20visa%20renewals%20are%20processed%20during%20the%20pilot%20phase%3B%20other%20visa%20types%20are%20not%20included.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20H-1B%20visa%20to%20be%20renewed%20must%20have%20been%20issued%20by%20Mission%20Canada%20between%20January%201%2C%202020%2C%20and%20April%201%2C%202023%2C%20or%20by%20Mission%20India%20from%20February%201%2C%202021%2C%20to%20September%2030%2C%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEligibility%20for%20a%20waiver%20of%20the%20in-person%20interview%20is%20required.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20have%20previously%20submitted%20ten%20fingerprints%20to%20the%20Department%20for%20a%20past%20visa%20application.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20should%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20a%20nonimmigrant%20visa%20issuance%20fee%2C%20also%20known%20as%20a%20reciprocity%20fee.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20prior%20visa%20must%20not%20have%20a%20'clearance%20received'%20annotation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20cannot%20have%20a%20visa%20ineligibility%20that%20requires%20a%20waiver%20for%20issuance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20have%20an%20approved%20and%20unexpired%20H-1B%20petition.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20applicant's%20most%20recent%20admission%20to%20the%20U.S.%20must%20have%20been%20in%20H-1B%20status.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20be%20currently%20maintaining%20H-1B%20status%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20period%20of%20authorized%20admission%20in%20H-1B%20status%20should%20not%20have%20expired.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20intend%20to%20reenter%20the%20U.S.%20in%20H-1B%20status%20after%20a%20temporary%20period%20abroad.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EH-1B%20Visa%20Pilot%20Programme%3A%20Application%20Details%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20submit%20applications%2C%20visit%20here%20(%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2Fcontent%2Ftravel%2Fen%2Fus-visas%2Femployment%2Fdomestic-renewal.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1703231553446000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3RLftzqZ8ucMPYutTV9wZq%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2Fcontent%2Ftravel%2Fen%2Fus-visas%2Femployment%2Fdomestic-renewal.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2F%3Cwbr%3Econtent%2Ftravel%2Fen%2Fus-visas%2F%3Cwbr%3Eemployment%2Fdomestic-renewal.%3Cwbr%3Ehtml%3C%2Fa%3E).%20An%20overview%20of%20this%20regulation%20is%20accessible%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.regulations.gov%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1703231553446000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0T8Tvqgnft997S_Zj8yO5e%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.regulations.gov%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewww.regulations.gov%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20searching%20for%20%26quot%3B1400-AF79%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20homepage.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnApplicants%20are%20required%20to%20pay%20the%20non-refundable%20and%20non-transferable%20MRV%20fee%20of%20%24205%20(Rs%2017%2C072)%20through%20the%20online%20portal.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20further%20inquiries%20or%20assistance%2C%20applicants%20can%20contact%20Jami%20Thompson%2C%20Senior%20Regulatory%20Coordinator%2C%20Visa%20Services%2C%20Bureau%20of%20Consular%20Affairs%2C%20Department%20of%20State%2C%20via%20email%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3AVisaRegs%40state.gov%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVisaRegs%40state.gov%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703146020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fjg7n7d98_h-1b-visa650-_625x300_05_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fh-1b-visa-pilot-programme-dates-eligibility-criteria-application-details-4715014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Department%20is%20introducing%20a%20pilot%20programme%20to%20restart%20the%20renewal%20process%20for%20qualified%20H-1B%20non-immigrant%20visa%20applicants%20within%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fh-1b-visa-pilot-programme-dates-eligibility-criteria-application-details-4715014%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fh-1b-visa-pilot-programme-dates-eligibility-criteria-application-details-4715014%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fh-1b-visa-pilot-programme-dates-eligibility-criteria-application-details-4715014%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Long-Lasting%20Legacy%20of%20Bhide%20Wada%2C%20Where%20the%20Phules%20Set%20Up%20Their%20First%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21132757%2FFH_m4ZgVIAMpUgL.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%205%2C%202023%2C%20Bhide%20Wada%2C%20an%20old%2C%20dilapidated%20historic%20building%20located%20at%20257%20Budhwar%20Peth%20in%20Pune%20City%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpune%2Fpolice-pmc-demolishes-bhide-wada-structure-jyotiba-phules-school-memorial-9055005%2F%5C%22%3Edemolished%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Pune%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(PMC).%20The%20structure%20housed%20the%20first%20indigenous%20girls%E2%80%99%20school%20of%20modern%20India%2C%20established%20by%20Savitribai%20and%20Jyotirao%20Phule%20in%201848.%20The%20state%20government%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20a%20national%20memorial%20on%20this%20site%20to%20commemorate%20the%20Phule%20couple%E2%80%99s%20significant%20contribution%20to%20modern%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20decades%20before%20its%20demolition%2C%20Bhide%20Wada%20stood%20as%20a%20modest%20and%20self-effacing%20structure%20to%20onlookers%20and%20people%20in%20the%20bustling%20neighbourhood.%20Bystanders%20who%20were%20oblivious%20to%20its%20historical%20significance%20may%20have%20thought%20of%20it%20as%20just%20another%20dilapidated%20building%20in%20the%20pool%20of%20many%20such%20structures%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20that%20required%20immediate%20repair%20and%20renovation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20PMC%20identified%20this%20building%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%20and%20unsafe%E2%80%9D%20for%20everyday%20use.%20Irrespective%20of%20its%20introverted%20and%20unassuming%20appearance%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20Bhide%20Wada%20represented%20a%20significant%20chapter%20in%20the%20history%20of%20modern%20India.%20Even%20after%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20school%20founded%20by%20Jyotirao%20Phule%2C%20Bhide%20Wada%20was%20an%20important%20centre%20of%20public%20activism%20in%20the%2019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20centuries.%20It%20frequently%20attracted%20prominent%20public%20figures%2C%20including%20Mahadev%20Govind%20Ranade%20and%20Dayanand%20Saraswati.%20Bhide%20Wada%20was%20a%20site%20that%20changed%20the%20lives%20of%20Savitribai%20and%20Jyotirao%20forever%20to%20become%20leading%20crusaders%20of%20equality%20and%20public%20education.%20Therefore%2C%20Bhide%20Wada%20cannot%20be%20simply%20forgotten%20as%20a%20monument%20of%20a%20bygone%20era%2C%20as%20it%20instrumentally%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20new%20political%20and%20cultural%20articulations%20in%20modern%20India.%20In%20a%20society%20that%20is%20overwhelmingly%20dominated%20by%20the%20practices%20of%20caste%20prejudices%2C%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20caste-based%20violence%2C%20Bhide%20Wada%20is%20a%20monument%20of%20alternative%20expression.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhide%20Wada%2C%20owned%20by%20the%20Bhide%20family%2C%20was%20constructed%20in%20a%20thriving%20business%20district%20of%20Budhwar%20Peth%20when%20the%20Peshwas%20ruled%20Pune%20before%20their%20eventual%20defeat%20in%201818.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWada%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(cottage)-like%20structures%2C%20constructed%20in%20different%20Peths%20or%20localities%2C%20became%20a%20familiar%20sight%20across%20the%20city%20in%20the%2018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%2019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20centuries.%20One%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Bhide%20family%2C%20Tatyasaheb%20Bhide%2C%20a%20strong%20sympathiser%20and%20a%20friend%20of%20Jotirao%20Phule%2C%20wanted%20to%20help%20him%20set%20up%20a%20school.%20He%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20passion%20and%20gave%20two%20rooms%20of%20his%20family%20cottage%20for%20the%20school%20premises.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20establishment%20of%20this%20school%20irked%20many%20traditionalists%20and%20deeply%20distressed%20Savitribai%2C%20Jyotirao%2C%20and%20their%20supporters.%20Here%2C%20Savitribai%20rose%20to%20the%20occasion%20and%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20that%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20educational%20activism%20in%20modern%20India.%20She%20was%20initially%20educated%20by%20Jyotirao%20and%20later%20completed%20teacher%20training%20courses%20to%20become%20a%20teacher%20and%20headmistress%20of%20the%20school%20located%20at%20Bhide%20Wada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20Bhide%20Wada%20school%20was%20a%20short-lived%20experiment%2C%20it%20created%20a%20long-lasting%20legacy.%20With%20time%2C%20the%20Phule%20couple%20established%20more%20than%2018%20schools%20across%20Pune.%20Savitribai%20and%20Jyotirao%20Phule%20became%20leading%20voices%20of%20radical%20anti-caste%20activism.%20Satyashodhak%20Samaj%2C%20founded%20by%20Jyotirao%2C%20was%20actively%20involved%20in%20voicing%20the%20grievances%20of%20the%20peasants%2C%20women%2C%20non-Brahmins%2C%20and%20the%20untouchables.%20Before%20launching%20the%20Satyashodhak%20Samaj%20in%201873%2C%20Phule%20established%20himself%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20potent%20critics%20of%20social%20conservatism%20and%20religious%20nationalism%20in%20Western%20India.%20Therefore%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20import%20of%20Phule%E2%80%99s%20activism%20and%20his%20radical%20stance%20against%20caste%20and%20patriarchy%2C%20the%20history%20of%20Bhide%20Wada%20cannot%20be%20forgotten.%20It%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20new%20voices%20of%20cultural%20expression%20that%20also%20foregrounded%20a%20new%20language%20of%20politics%20in%20modern%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21133019%2Fjyotirao-and-savitribai.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21133019%2Fjyotirao-and-savitribai.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21133019%2Fjyotirao-and-savitribai-300x213.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21133019%2Fjyotirao-and-savitribai-1024x726.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690147%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22851%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBusts%20of%20Mahatma%20Jyotirao%20Phule%20and%20Savitribai%20Phule.%20Photo%3A%20Priyanka%20bhise%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20time%2C%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%202%2C500%20sq%20ft%20Bhide%20Wada%20changed%20from%20one%20owner%20to%20the%20other%20in%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century.%20We%20find%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20sale%20deed%20of%201924%20that%20mentioned%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20land%20from%20Sadashiv%20Narayan%20Bhide%20to%20the%20Mavadikar%20family.%20Subsequently%2C%20Bhide%20Wada%20was%20sold%20in%20two%20phases%20to%20Pune-based%20Poune%20Merchants%20Co-operative%20Bank%20in%201969%20and%201972.%20In%202000%2C%20the%20bank%20requested%20a%20real%20estate%20firm%20to%20redevelop%20the%20property.%20After%20substantial%20redevelopment%2C%20the%20work%20was%20halted%20by%20a%20stay%20order%20in%202005.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20interesting%20aspect%20of%20this%20entire%20chronicle%20of%20Bhide%20Wada%20is%20how%20some%20historical%20sites%20associated%20with%20Dalit-OBC%20assertions%20have%20been%20conveniently%20forgotten%20in%20post-independence%20India.%20It%20took%20more%20than%2050%20years%20after%20independence%20for%20the%20state%20institutions%20to%20recognise%20the%20importance%20of%20Bhide%20Wada.%20In%202006%2C%20after%20continuous%20demands%20from%20different%20quarters%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20PMC%20and%20the%20state%20government%20finally%20proposed%20a%20plan%20to%20set%20up%20a%20national%20monument%20to%20commemorate%20the%20contributions%20of%20the%20Phule%20couple.%20After%2013%20years%20of%20protracted%20legal%20battle%20with%20its%20occupants%2C%20the%20site%20was%20finally%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20PMC%20through%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fpune-news%2Fhandover-bhide-wada-to-pmc-within-a-month-sc-to-owners-tenants-101698940794627.html%5C%22%3Eintervention%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20monuments%20like%20Bhide%20Wada%20are%20ignored%20highlights%20how%20histories%20of%20anti-caste%20and%20Dalit-Bahujan%20politics%20are%20still%20rendered%20unacceptable%20to%20mainstream%20frameworks.%20The%20Dalit-Bahujan%20attempts%20at%20memorialisation%20are%20often%20ridiculed%20and%20treated%20as%20manifestations%20of%20emotional%20and%20irrational%20deifications.%20It%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20until%201990%2C%20there%20was%20no%20portrait%20of%20Ambedkar%20in%20the%20central%20hall%20of%20the%20parliament.%20Simultaneously%2C%20it%20was%20only%20after%20continuous%20campaigns%20conducted%20across%20Maharashtra%20from%20the%201980s%20onwards%20that%20the%20historical%20sites%20associated%20with%20Jyotirao%20and%20Savitribai%20Phule%20were%20converted%20into%20protected%20monuments.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20unlike%20Bhide%20Wada%2C%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20monuments%20in%20Maharashtra%20seldom%20depend%20on%20state%20patronage%20and%20support.%20Monuments%20like%20Chaitya%20Bhoomi%20and%20Deekshabhoomi%20have%20become%20significant%20sites%20of%20assertion%20that%20help%20the%20erstwhile%20untouchables%20navigate%20beyond%20stigma%20and%20humiliation.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20memorialisation%20of%20the%20monuments%20associated%20with%20the%20anti-caste%20movement%20is%20essential%20for%20Dalit%20and%20OBC%20movements%20to%20steer%20through%20dominant%20interpretations%20of%20culture.%20Creating%20such%20sites%20of%20memorialisation%20also%20helps%20democratise%20the%20overall%20political%20and%20cultural%20ambience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20monuments%20like%20Bhide%20Wada%20are%20not%20just%20physical%20structures.%20They%20can%20pose%20a%20real%20challenge%20to%20the%20dominant%20forms%20of%20power.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20if%20Bhide%20Wada%20becomes%20a%20temple%20of%20deification%20of%20Savitribai%20and%20Jyotirao%2C%20it%20will%20generate%20counterproductive%20results.%20In%20the%20new%20context%2C%20whatever%20affirmative%20feelings%20it%20evokes%2C%20there%20is%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20such%20sites%20becoming%20banal%20and%20apolitical%20locations%20of%20identity%20creation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprabodhan-pol%5C%22%3EPrabodhan%20Pol%3C%2Fa%3E%20teaches%20at%20Manipal%20Centre%20for%20Humanities%20MAHE%2C%20Manipal%20(Karnataka).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703145922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21132757%2FFH_m4ZgVIAMpUgL.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%