ase%20of%20over%201.13%20lakh%20individuals%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fover-20000-attempts-to-hack-crowd-funding-site-in-past-2-days-claims-congress-2820090%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20donors%2C%2032%20individuals%20contributed%20more%20than%20Rs%20one%20lakh%2C%20with%20notable%20names%20including%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20and%20Pawan%20Khera.%20More%20than%20600%20people%20donated%20Rs%2013%2C800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maximum%20contributions%20came%20from%20Maharashtra%20(Rs%2056%20lakh)%2C%20followed%20by%20Rajasthan%20(Rs%2026%20lakh)%2C%20Delhi%20(Rs%2020%20lakh)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(Rs%2019%20lakh)%20and%20Karnataka%20(Rs%2018%20lakh)%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20party%20leader%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%2C%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20donors%20from%20Bihar%20made%20contributions%20in%20smaller%20denominations%20reflecting%20a%20broad%20base%20of%20support%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20donation%20website%2C%20www.donateinc.in%2C%20attracted%20an%20audience%20of%201.2%20crore%20visitors%20in%20the%20initial%2048%20hours.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20followed%20by%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20cyber%20attacks%2C%20including%201%2C340%20attempts%20to%20steal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fover-20000-attempts-to-hack-crowd-funding-site-in-past-2-days-claims-congress-2820090%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20had%20anticipated%20these%20attacks%20and%20implemented%20robust%20firewalls%20to%20tackle%20this%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20breakdown%20of%20the%20payment%20preferences%20of%20donors%20showed%20that%2081%25%20chose%20the%20UPI%20route%2C%20followed%20by%20credit%20cards%20(7.95%25)%2C%20debit%20cards%20(6.3