20EPFO%20data%20to%20analyse%20employment%20trends%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2068.7%25%20(5%2C30%2C884)%20of%20the%20total%207%2C72%2C084%20who%20joined%20the%20workforce%20in%20October%20were%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018-28%20age%2C%20accounting%20for%20the%20highest%20among%20new%20EPF%20subscribers%20in%20October.%20The%20same%20figure%20had%20stood%20at%2068.5%25%20in%20the%20previous%20month%20of%20September%2C%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Ffresh-formal-job-creation-dips-to-7-month-low-in-october-shows-epfo-data-123122001097_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0quoting%20official%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20those%20who%20joined%20the%20workforce%20and%20registered%20themselves%20as%20new%20EPF%20subscribers%20in%20the%20age%20group%20above%2035%20reduced%20from%2016.1%25%20in%20September%20to%2015.9%25%20in%20October.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20share%2C%20however%2C%20saw%20a%20marginal%20increase%20from%2025.2%25%20in%20September%20to%2026.4%25%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20net%20payroll%20addition%20increased%20by%201%25%2C%20taking%20the%20number%20from%201.51%20million%20in%20September%20to%201.53%20million%20in%20October.%20The%20net%20payroll%20figure%20is%20worked%20out%20by%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20number%20of%20new%20subscribers%2C%20the%20number%20of%20exits%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20old%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%20for%20the%20months%20under%20consideration%20also%20indicated%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20unemployment%20rate.%20According%20to%20CMIE%E2%80%99s%20Consumer%20Pyramids%20Household%20Survey%2C%20it%20shot%20from%207.09%25%20in%20September%20to%2010.09%25%20in%20October.%20The%20rise%20in%20joblessness%20was%20attributed%20to%20a%20sharp%20jump%20in%20the%20rural