er.%20%26quot%3BCurrently%2C%20MiG-29%20jets%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INS%20Vikrant%20fighter%20fleet.%20The%20state-of-the-art%20French%20fighter%20jets%20Rafale-M%20will%20replace%20MiG-29s%2C''%20Navy%20chief%20Admiral%20R%20Hari%20Kumar%20said%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavy%20sources%20have%20said%20there%20is%20every%20possibility%20of%20China%20operating%20a%20carrier%20battle%20group%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20The%20decision%20to%20get%20Rafale%20jets%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20against%20this%20backdrop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20already%20operates%20its%20first%20overseas%20base%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20in%20Djibouti%2C%20where%20it%20has%20started%20docking%20warships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20had%20last%20year%20sourced%20satellite%20images%20that%20indicated%20that%20China's%20naval%20base%20in%20Djibouti%2C%20on%20the%20Horn%20of%20Africa%2C%20is%20fully%20operational%20and%20supports%20Chinese%20warships%20deployed%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20base%20in%20Djibouti%20is%20its%20first%20overseas%20military%20base%2C%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20%24590%20million.%20It%20is%20located%20by%20the%20strategic%20Bab-El-Mandeb%20Strait%20which%20separates%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20guards%20the%20approach%20to%20the%20Suez%20Canal%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20critical%20channels%20of%20international%20commerce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Djibouti%20base%20%26quot%3Bis%20built%20in%20a%20fortified%20way%2C%20with%20layers%20of%20defences%20which%20appear%20almost%20medieval%2C%20like%20a%20modern%20day%20colonial%20fort.%20It%20is%20clearly%20designed%20to%20withstand%20direct%20assault%2C''%20says%20Naval%20Analyst%20HI%20Sutton%20of%20Covert%20Shores.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703142540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fptaol9r8_rafale-pic_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http