es%2Fcj5g2nzeryvo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcj5g2nzeryvo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndia%20On%20Verge%20Of%20Take-Off%2C%20Indians%20Want%20Flight%20To%20Be%20Expedited%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExuding%20confidence%20in%20returning%20to%20his%207%20Lok%20Kalyan%20Marg%20residence%20for%20a%20third%2C%20straight%20term%20in%20office%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20his%20fellow%20citizens%20have%20come%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20country%20is%20poised%20for%20a%20giant%20leap%20and%20want%20their%20aspirations%20to%20take%20wings%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20swept%20three%20heartland%20states%20--%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20--%20that%20went%20to%20Assembly%20polls%20last%20month%2C%20building%20a%20good%20head%20of%20steam%20and%20electoral%20momentum%20going%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20UK-based%20daily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F160235af-1584-4ec7-8aad-a3de70753f30%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20the%20Indians%20now%20appreciate%20and%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20country%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20take-off%20and%20want%20%26quot%3Bthis%20flight%20to%20be%20expedited%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remark%20is%20being%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20next%20general%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20between%20April%20and%20May%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20confident%20of%20victory%26quot%3B%2C%20invoking%20his%20government's%20track%20record%20in%20bringing%20%26quot%3Bsolid%20change%20in%20the%20common%20man's%20life%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20very%20different%20aspirations%20from%20the%20ones%20they%20had%2010%20years%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20realise%20that%20our%20nation%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20a%20take-off.%20They%20want%20this%20flight%20to%20be%20expedited%2C%20and%20they%20know%20the%20best%20party%20to%20ensure%20this%20is%20the%20one%20which%20brought%20them%20this%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20Assembly%20elections%20to%20five%20states%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20PM%20Modi%20at%20the%20front%20and%20centre%20of%20its%20campaign%20pitch%2C%20won%20resounding%20mandates%20in%20the%20heartland%20states%2C%20stumping%20not%20just%20their%20rivals%20but%20also%20some%20pollsters%20who%20had%20predicted%20tight%20races%20in%20MP%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20swept%20Rajasthan%2C%20defying%20exit-poll%20projections%20of%20a%20tight%20race%20and%20winning%20115%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20came%20a%20distant%20second%20with%2069%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20first-time%20MLA%20from%20Sanganer%2C%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20took%20the%20oath%20as%20the%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20on%20December%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiya%20Kumari%20and%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%20were%20also%20sworn%20in%20as%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20of%20the%20desert%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20neighbouring%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Vishnu%20Sai%2C%20who%20won%20four%20consecutive%20terms%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20the%20Raigarh%20constituency%20from%201999%20to%202014%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20chief%20minister%20on%20December%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2090%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20BJP%20bagged%2054%20while%20the%20tally%20of%20the%20incumbent%2C%20Congress%2C%20was%20reduced%20to%2035.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20despite%20battling%20close%20to%2020%20years%20of%20anti-incumbency%2C%20won%20a%20rousing%20mandate%2C%20bagging%20163%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20sa