3012.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What's%20Behind%20Latest%20Covid%20Spike%3F%20Experts%20On%20Whether%20It's%20Time%20To%20Mask%20Up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20rise%20in%20daily%20Covid%20case%20counts%20and%20several%20states%20issuing%20mask%20advisories%20have%20brought%20back%20grim%20memories%20of%20the%20pandemic%20that%20locked%20us%20indoors%20and%20wrapped%20us%20in%20fear%20for%20two%20years.%20A%20total%20of%20358%20Covid%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20across%20the%20country%20in%20the%20past%2024%20hours%2C%20300%20of%20them%20in%20Kerala.%20Six%20people%20died%20due%20to%20Covid-related%20complications%20during%20this%20period.%20The%20country%20has%202%2C669%20active%20cases%20of%20Covid%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Union%20Health%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20Covid%20count%20of%20614%20cases%20reported%20yesterday%2C%20the%20highest%20since%20May%2C%20set%20off%20alarm%20bells.%20This%20spike%20in%20infections%20is%20driven%20by%20a%20Covid%20variant%20named%20JN.1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20has%20classified%20JN.1%20as%20a%20'variant%20of%20interest'%20but%20said%20that%20evidence%20currently%20available%20suggests%20that%20it%20does%20not%20pose%20a%20major%20risk.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20this%2C%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20winter%20in%20the%20Northern%20Hemisphere%2C%20JN.1%20could%20increase%20the%20burden%20of%20respiratory%20infections%20in%20many%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20WHO%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdr-soumya-swaminathan-jn-1-covid-variant-30-of-those-with-flu-like-illnesses-in-kochi-hospitals-are-covid-positive-top-expert-4712147%5C%22%3EDr%20Soumya%20Swaminathan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20WHO%20chief%20scientist%2C%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20on%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20spike%20in%20Covid%20infections.%20She%20cautioned%20against%20dismissing%20Covid%20as%20a%20common%20cold%2C%20not%20just%20because%20of%20people%20who%20fall%20severely%20ill%2C%20but%20because%20of%20the%20disease's%20long-term%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%2030%25%20of%20pneumonia%20cases%20in%20Kochi%20hospitals%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20Covid%20positive%20and%20the%20likelihood%20of%20this%20being%20replicated%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20through%20this%20many%20times%20before%2C%20as%20you%20know%2C%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20This%20is%20what%20we%20expected%20and%20this%20is%20what%20the%20WHO%20had%20talked%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20a%20new%20variant%2C%20the%20JN.1%2C%20which%20is%20a%20sub-variant%20of%20Omicron.%20So%20hopefully%20it%20behaves%20like%20Omicron%2C%20which%20was%20relatively%20mild.%20But%20what%20happens%20is%20that%20every%20new%20variant%20gets%20some%20properties%20of%20being%20more%20transmissible.%20It%20is%20able%20to%20evade%20or%20avoid%20the%20antibody%20responses%20that%20we%20already%20have%20in%20our%20system.%20And%20therefore%20it%20is%20able%20to%20create%20these%20waves%20of%20infection%20where%20it%20infects%20people%20who've%20already%20been%20infected%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20comparing%20newer%20variants%20of%20Covid%20with%20the%20common%20cold%2C%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20had%20a%20warning%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20different%20from%20the%20common%20cold%2C%20not%20just%20because%20of%20people%20getting%20severely%20ill%20with%20acute%20Covid%20pneumonia%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20the%20long-term%20effects%20of%20Covid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20we%20have%20enough%20data%20now%20from%20around%20the%20world%20to%20know%20that%20people%20who%20have%20suffered%20from%20Covid%20and%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20have%20repeat%20infections%2C%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%2C%20for%20example%2C%20heart%20attacks%2C%20strokes%2C%20diabetes%2C%20dementia%2C%20depression%2C%20mental%20health%20problems%2C%20prolonged%20fatigue%20and%20muscle%20pain...%20inability%20to%20go%20back%20to%20their%20usual%20state%20of%20functioning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swaminathan%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20would%20say%20let's%20not%20take%20it%20lightly.%20If%20you%20can%20avoid%20the%20infection%2C%20much%20better%20to%20avoid%20it%20than%20to%20get%20it%20and%20risk%20the%20after-effects%20of%20long%20Covid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rajeev%20Jayadevan%2C%20Co-Chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20Covid%20Task%20Force%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20vaccines%20may%20have%20helped%20keep%20Covid%20at%20bay%20since%20the%20last%20wave%2C%20but%20a%20concern%20arises%20when%20a%20variant%20is%20markedly%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20JN.1%20is%20not%20like%20a%20one-step%20ahead%20variant.%20This%20is%20a%20multi-step%20ahead%20variant.%20We%20call%20it%20the%20saltation%20event%20in%20genetics%2C%20which%20basically%20means%20a%20pile%20of%20mutations%20suddenly%20occurring%20at%20one%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20masking%20up%2C%20he%20advised%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20if%20you%20are%20trapped%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20it's%20ventilated%2C%20closed%2C%20crowded%2C%20you%20feel%20the%20air%20is%20still%20and%20there%20are%20people%20around%20you%2C%20it's%20safer%20to%20wear%20a%20mask.%20If%20you%20are%20travelling%20in%20a%20vehicle%20with%20multiple%20people%20who%20you%20don't%20know%2C%20wear%20a%20mask%20or%20at%20least%20roll%20your%20windows%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swaminathan%20said%20the%20symptoms%20of%20the%20JN.1%20variant%20are%20fever%2C%20cough%2C%20loss%20of%20smell%20and%20loss%20of%20taste.%20She%20also%20pointed%20to%20persistent%20high%20fever%2C%20breathing%20difficulties%2C%20fatigue%2C%20inability%20to%20eat%20and%20a%20tendency%20to%20vomit%20as%20the%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swaminathan%20recommended%20masking%20up%20in%20a%20crowded%20place%20if%20people%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20infections%20and%20also%20stressed%20that%20people%20who%20are%20sick%20should%20wear%20a%20mask%20to%20protect%20others.%20For%20the%20vulnerable%20population%2C%20she%20recommended%20using%20pulse%20oximeters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20not%20let%20the%20guard%20down%2C%20the%20Union%20Health%20Ministry%20held%20a%20high-level%20review%20of%20the%20situation%20in%20India%20and%20preparations%20to%20tackle%20any%20spike%20caused%20by%20the%20new%20Covid%20variant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20Minister%20Dr%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20to%20be%20alert%20and%20prepared%20against%20new%20and%20emerging%20strains%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20virus%26quot%3B.%20He%20asked%20all%20states%20to%20remain%20alert%2C%20step%20up%20surveillance%20and%20ensure%20adequate%20stock%20of%20medicines%2C%20oxygen%20cylinders%20and%20other%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20of%20Chandigarh%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%2C%20asking%20people%20to%20wear%20mask%20in%20crowded%20and%20closed%20settings%20and%20to%20practise%20hand%20hygiene%20amid%20the%20spike%20in%20Covid%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703137260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F50u917tg_covid-mask_625x300_21_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovid-spike-jn-1-whats-behind-latest-covid-spike-experts-on-whether-its-time-to-mask-up-4714343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20rise%20in%20daily%20Covid%20case%20counts%20and%20several%20states%20issuing%20mask%20advisories%20have%20brought%20back%20grim%20memories%20of%20the%20pandemic%20that%20locked%20us%20indoors%20and%20wrapped%20us%20in%20fear%20for%20two%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%