0with%20enthusiasm%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20where%20mergers%20of%20legacy%20media%20companies%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%20And%20WBD%20doesn't%20own%20a%20broadcast%20network%2C%20which%20means%20its%20acquisition%20of%20Paramount's%20CBS%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20major%20regulatory%20issue%20%E2%80%94%20as%20would%20be%20the%20case%20if%20NBC%20parent%20Comcast%20were%20to%20make%20a%20deal%20to%20acquire%20Paramount%2C%20as%20some%20media%20observers%20have%20speculated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeedham%20analyst%20Laura%20Martin%20for%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthedesk.net%2F2023%2F11%2Fparamount-needham-analyst-sell-to-warner-bros-discovery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etalked%20up%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Paramount%20sale%20to%20WBD%20in%20November%2C%20saying%20its%20valuable%20assets%20could%20be%20a%20good%20fit%20with%20a%20bigger%20company.%20Paramount's%20CBS%20and%20WBD's%20CNN%20together%20would%20make%20a%20formidable%20news%20organization%2C%20and%20the%20companies'%20streaming%20services%20%E2%80%94%20Paramount%2B%20and%20Max%20%E2%80%94%20have%20complementary%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20shares%20of%20both%20companies%20declined%20today%20amid%20news%20of%20the%20talks%2C%20Warner%20by%205.6%25%20and%20Paramount%20by%202%25%2C%20and%20other%20analysts%20threw%20cold%20water%20on%20a%20deal%20being%20a%20cure-all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsolidation%20won't%20fix%20legacy%20media's%20streaming%20woes%2C%20LightShed%20Partners%20argued%20in%20a%20December%2019%20note.%20They're%20too%20late%20and%20lack%20the%20talent%20and%20strategy%20to%20build%20scaled%20streamers%20while%20managing%20their%20linear%20TV%20declines%2C%20and%20layering%20on%20more%20linear%20TV%20assets%20to%20a%20WBD%20or%20Paramount%20%26quot%3Bfeels%20like%20a%20financial%20death%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20LightShed%20wrote.%20LightShed's%20Richard%20Greenfield%20doubled%20down%20on%20that%20argument%20Wednesday%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D