E%3Cp%3ESince%20October%202022%2C%20I've%20been%20live%20selling%20as%20a%20side%20hustle.%20That%20means%20hosting%20livestreams%20on%20TikTok%20Shop%2C%20where%20I%20sell%20everything%20from%20televisions%20to%20air%20purifiers%20to%20computers%20directly%20to%20the%20viewer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20this%20year%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20was%20making%20about%20the%20same%20amount%20from%20both%20my%20main%20and%20side%20hustle.%20My%20salary%20in%20my%20old%20job%20was%20around%205%2C500%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20%244%2C000%2C%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20I%20was%20exhausted%20splitting%20my%20attention%20between%20both%2C%20I%20figured%20it%20was%20time%20to%20make%20a%20switch%20to%20livestreaming%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20hours%20of%20nonstop%20talking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jotham%20Lim's%20livestreams%20on%20TikTok%20Shop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657ac35d7a3c8094d5dcd7af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJotham%20Lim's%20livestreams%20on%20TikTok%20Shop.%3Cp%3EJotham%20Tobiah%20Lim%20Jin%20Han%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20livestream%20lasts%20between%20two%20to%20four%20hours%2C%20with%20anywhere%20from%2020%20to%20400%20people%20watching%20at%20any%20one%20time%20%E2%80%94%20or%20between%201%2C400%20to%207%2C000%20unique%20viewers%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20I'm%20usually%20flying%20solo%20and%20talking%20non-stop.%20That%20includes%20describing%20the%20deals%2C%20showing%20off%20the%20products%2C%20answering%20questions%20%E2%80%94%20about%20both%20myself%20and%20the%20thing%20I'm%20selling%20%E2%80%94%20and%20just%20being%20really%20high-energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20whole%20process%20from%20clicking%20on%20a%20product%20to%20checkout%2C%20the%20viewer%20is%20still%20hearing%20my%20voice.%20It's