5C%22What%20the%20TikTok%20Shop%20dashboard%20looks%20like%20during%20a%20livestream.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657befdc0ec98e92f74fd60f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhat%20the%20TikTok%20Shop%20dashboard%20looks%20like%20during%20a%20livestream.%3Cp%3EJotham%20Tobiah%20Lim%20Jin%20Han%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20of%20TikTok%20Shop%20is%20that%20during%20the%20livestream%2C%20you're%20looking%20at%20a%20dashboard%20with%20all%20these%20stats%20on%20how%20long%20viewers%20are%20watching%2C%20their%20demographics%2C%20and%20what%20they're%20buying.%20So%20you%20get%20a%20good%20understanding%20of%20what%20works%2C%20and%20what%20doesn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnswering%20questions%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20it.%20Some%20viewers%20are%20genuinely%20interested%20in%20the%20product%2C%20but%20others%20are%20less%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20can%20ask%20pretty%20intrusive%20questions%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20attached%3F%26quot%3B.%20And%20some%20internet%20trolls%20come%20on%20just%20to%20throw%20insults%20at%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManaging%20these%20in%20a%20fun%20way%20is%20part%20of%20the%20gig.%20I've%20found%20that%20viewers%20love%20it%20when%20you%20bring%20the%20drama%20and%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20trolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EViewers%20tune%20in%20for%20time-sensitive%20discounts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jotham%20Lim%20during%20his%20livestreams.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657bf0b47a3c8094d5dd5bbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJotham%20Lim%20during%20his%20livestreams.%3Cp%3EJotham%20Tobiah%20Lim%20Jin%20Han%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20every%20livestream%2C%20I%20have%20a%20discussion%20with%20the%20company%20that's%20hiring%20me%20to%20understand%20the