0an%20adjustable%20hem%2C%20two-way%20zippers%2C%20a%20durable%20water-resistant%20outer%20lining%2C%20and%20adjustable%20sleeves.%20And%20the%20most%20surprising%20feature%20of%20all%20is%20that%20it's%20packable%20%E2%80%94%20something%20unheard%20of%20for%20jackets%20this%20big.%20In%20terms%20of%20function%2C%20I%20can't%20think%20of%20a%20single%20feature%20I%20wish%20it%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Expedition%20Down%20Jacket%20is%20as%20no-nonsense%20as%20winter%20coats%20come%2C%20its%20oversized%20fit%20makes%20it%20less%20practical%20for%20daily%20use.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20found%20it%20uncomfortable%20and%20difficult%20to%20drive%20my%20car%20while%20wearing%20it.%20If%20you%20love%20the%20style%2C%20but%20want%20a%20jacket%20that's%20a%20bit%20more%20practical%20(and%20affordable)%2C%20I%20also%20recommend%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fjallraven.com%2Fus%2Fen-us%2Fmen%2Fjackets%2Fwinter-jackets%2Fexpedition-down-lite-jacket-m%3Fv%3DF84605%253a%253a7323450930455%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExpedition%20Down%20Lite%20Jacket%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20waterproof%3A%20Marmot%20GORE-TEX%20Mammoth%20Parka%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221636%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20car%20wearing%20the%20Marmot%20GORE-TEX%20Mammoth%20Parka.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658360b5a79e5746976bf05a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221229%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDown%20fill%20power%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20700%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExterior%20fabric%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Waterproof%2C%20breathable%202-layer%20GORE-TEX%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%203%20lbs%2C%205%20oz%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHood%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Removable%20hood%20with%20adjustable