Fbeyonce-self-titled-10-year-anniversary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20first%20visual%20album%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20practice%20in%20mood-building%20as%20much%20as%20storytelling.%20It%20opened%20with%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLXXQLa-5n5w%3Fsi%3DJJvPw4iCk1cX7PgJ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPretty%20Hurts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20boldfaced%20critique%20of%20modernity.%20(To%20continue%20the%20line%20of%20symmetry%2C%20Cyrus%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20both%20had%20banner%20years%20in%202023%20with%20%26quot%3BEndless%20Summer%20Vacation%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Renaissance%20World%20Tour%2C%20respectively.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22miley%20cyrus%20adore%20you%20river%20music%20videos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658228611c5c7b8c9a0a16b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMiley%20Cyrus%20in%20%26quot%3BAdore%20You%26quot%3B%20(2013)%20and%20%26quot%3BRiver%26quot%3B%20(2023).%3Cp%3EMiley%20Cyrus%2FYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20distinct%20and%20different%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20the%20albums%20and%20songs%20of%202013%20shared%20a%20self-conscious%20quality%20%E2%80%94%20hyper-aware%20of%20perception%20and%20pageantry%20%E2%80%94%20that%20felt%2C%20at%20least%20to%20my%20teenage%20brain%2C%20novel%20and%20era-defining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20the%20power%20of%20the%20digital%2C%20visual%20space%20has%20swelled%20beyond%20hyperbole.%20These%20days%2C%20particularly%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2022%2F12%2F26%2F23519605%2Ftiktok-viral-videos-privacy-surveillance-street-interviews-vlogs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20dominance%20of%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20real%20life%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20staging%20ground%20for%20social%20media%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20ominous%20u