20any%20such%20announcement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETeli%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20such%20announcement%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20Rajasthan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20discrepancy%20comes%20shortly%20after%20the%20BJP%20included%20the%20Rs%20450%20LPG%20cylinder%20pledge%20in%20its%20manifesto%20ahead%20of%20the%20November%20assembly%20elections.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHome%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20also%20publicly%20reiterated%20this%20commitment%20in%20a%20rally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffarmers-women-corruption-and-jobs-comparing-congress-bjps-rajasthan-manifestos%5C%22%3EFarmers%2C%20Women%2C%20Corruption%20and%20Jobs%3A%20Comparing%20Congress%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rajasthan%20Manifestos%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2022%2C%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20in%20a%20rally%2C%20had%20promised%20the%20women%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20the%20price%20of%20the%20cylinder%20increase%2C%20but%20the%20women%20in%20Rajasthan%20will%20still%20have%20access%20to%20it%20for%20Rs%20450.%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dt1ruuVzCvUM%5C%22%3E%5BSee%20video.%20Time%20stamp%3A%2020%3A55%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20public%20reaffirmation%20by%20Shah%20was%20intended%20to%20counter%20the%20existing%20Congress%20party%20scheme%2C%20where%20over%2076%20lakh%20families%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%20were%20already%20benefiting%20from%20LPG%20cylinders%20priced%20at%20Rs%20500%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20in%20its%20manifesto%2C%20had%20gone%20further%2C%20promising%20to%20reduce%20the%20LPG%20cylinder%20price%20to%20Rs%20400%20in%20Rajasthan.%20It%20had%20also%20promised%20to%20expan