20unemployment%20and%20inflation%20while%20the%20home%20minister%20has%20not%20made%20any%20statement%20in%20parliament%2C%20despite%20the%20opposition%20demanding%20it.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20rather%20than%20seeing%20the%20obvious%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20this%20act%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20breach%E2%80%9D%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20find%20the%20elements%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20the%20chink%20in%20the%20armour%20of%20the%20security%20system%20in%20parliament%20has%20been%20exposed%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20vulnerable%20to%20even%20minor%20attempts%20like%20that%20of%20these%20young%20individuals.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20has%20highlighted%20the%20need%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20rather%20than%20seeing%20it%20as%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20these%20individuals%20are%20not%20part%20of%20any%20terror%20group.%20Mercifully%2C%20none%20of%20the%20involved%20youth%20is%20a%20Muslim%2C%20neither%20do%20they%20belong%20to%20any%20terror-related%20organisation.%20The%20latter%20would%20have%20given%20an%20unfortunate%20boost%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20those%20out%20to%20intensify%20Islamophobia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20it%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20just%20pay%20lip%20service%20to%20Bhagat%20Singh.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20concern%20for%20the%20deprived%20sections%20of%20society%20needs%20to%20be%20highlighted.%20Let%20us%20remember%20that%20mass%20movements%20were%20central%20to%20his%20ideology.%20The%20path%20of%20violence%20was%20abandoned%20by%20him.%20He%20had%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20we%20can%20achieve%20independence%20only%20through%20mass%20mobilisation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201929%2C%20his%20attack%20was%20intended%20solely%20to%20make%20the%20%E2%80%98deaf%20hear%2C%E2%80%99%20not%20to%20harm%20anyone.%20It%20is%20heartening%20to%20note%20that%20our%20youth%20are%20turning%20to%20Bhagat%20Singh%20for%20guidance%20in%20the%20current%20troubled%20times%20and%20that%20many%20groups%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Bhagat%20Singh%20have%20sprung%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20entire%20episode%20should%20be%20approached%20with%20the%20right%20spirit%2C%20unlike%20the%20attempts%20by%20Godi%20media%20to%20portray%20them%20as%20villains.%20The%20aim%20of%20the%20youth%20is%20crystal%20clear%3B%20their%20inspiration%20is%20not%20from%20any%20ideology%20of%20terror%20but%20from%20the%20greatest%20revolutionary%20of%20our%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20four%20adopted%20a%20wrong%20method%2C%20their%20anguish%20should%20be%20recognised.%20Their%20aim%20of%20revising%20our%20%E2%80%98employment%20generation%E2%80%99%20policy%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20a%20serious%20look%2C%20rather%20than%20searching%20for%20a%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fram-puniyani%5C%22%3ERam%20Puniyani%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703082619000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F30163914%2FUntitled-design-6-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpangs-of-unemployment-why-indias-youth-is-turning-to-bhagat-singh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20four%20have%20been%20booked%20under%20UAPA%2C%20this%20incident%20is%20the%20most%20powerful%20attempt%20to%20bring%20the%20issue%20of%20rising%20unemployment%20to%20natio