-critical-you-are-a-threat-journalist-fighting-uapa-case-wins-global-press-award-656406ada874a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine%20of%20those%20accused%2C%20eight%20men%20and%20one%20woman%20%E2%80%93%20Saleem%2C%20Sharjeel%20Imam%2C%20Abdul%20Khali%20Saifi%2C%20Gulfisha%20Fatima%2C%20Meeran%20Haider%2C%20Salim%20Malik%2C%20Shifa%20Ur%20Rehman%2C%20Shadab%20Ahmed%20and%20Athar%20Khan%20%E2%80%93%20remain%20in%20jail%20after%20being%20denied%20bail%20by%20lower%20courts%2C%20their%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20denial%20of%20bail%20also%20pending%20for%2011%20to%2019%20months%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20a%20special%20bench%20consisting%20of%20Justice%20Siddharth%20Mridul%20and%20Justice%20Rajnish%20Bhatnagar%20listed%20the%20nine%20bail%20petitions%20for%20hearing%20between%2034%20and%2060%20times%20since%20April%202022%20and%20even%20concluded%20hearings%20and%20reserved%20judgements%20in%20six%20between%20January%20and%20March%202023%20%E2%80%93%20petitions%20of%20Saifi%2C%20Fatima%2C%20Haider%2C%20Malik%2C%20Rehman%2C%20and%20Saleem%20%E2%80%93%20it%20failed%20to%20deliver%20a%20final%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine%20cases%20came%20to%20a%20standstill%20when%2C%20on%20July%205%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20collegium%20recommended%20Justice%20Mridul%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20to%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20as%20its%20chief%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20cleared%20three%20months%20later%20on%20October%2016%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%20little%20more%20than%20a%20month%20later%2C%20Justice%20Bhatnagar%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20to%20the%20Rajasthan%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20and%20Justice%20Shalinder%20Kaur%20will%20now%20hear%20the%20nine%20cases%20afresh%2C%20further%20prolonging%20incarceration.%20On%20November%201%2C%202023%2C%20Justices%20Kait%20and%20Kaur%20fixed%20dates